{
  "stem": "1680.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all the school buildings and all the churches, everything was occupied by the armies, sometimes by our own armies, sometimes by the enemy armies, because it was going back and forth at that time.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in 1919, when the war broke out, then came a little war between Poland and Russia.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when Poland became a state in 1918, Russia didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they wanted to invade.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there was another war between Russia and Poland, which took about a year and a half.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at that time, one of my brothers, Moishe, was in the army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was running away, because he didn't want to serve for the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that was a whole commotion.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that was no time for me to school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in the 1923, when my father passed away, yeah, in the beginning, when they opened up the schools, there was no teachers.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was a teacher that she might have-- maybe have finished her fourth grade.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She didn't know from anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then was very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So Jews weren't allow to-- not they weren't allowed-- they were allowed to attend, but they insisted they should sit without caps.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the Jewish people didn't want this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So none of the Jewish people went to school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I was taught-- my father hired a teacher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I was taught privately with another boy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They brought in a teacher from another town, a Jewish teacher.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he taught us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then in 1923, I went for Tarnow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had-- we were nine originally.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when the war broke out, we were only five.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One of my brothers was-- came back from the first army and he died, because he had a sickness from the army.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was in 1917.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
